{"tid":53774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國遼寧號等8艘艦艇準備穿越第一島鏈","createTime":"2016-12-25T03:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T14:51:12.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12fc23fa094c6feb85745c54e61f889961d3a2ce","tid":53774,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:35:29.000Z","msg":"中國遼寧號等8艘艦艇準備穿越第一島鏈<br />\n<br />\n時間Sun Dec 25 09:59:45 2016<br />\n<br />\n日本防衛省今天表示日本海上自衛隊艦艇在昨天24號下午4點左右發現中國航母遼寧號在 東中國海出現，另外有7艘海軍艦艇所組成的艦隊在側準備往東航行。 日本防衛省不清楚其動向，但預測其將由日本近海駛入西太平洋，海上自衛隊目前正嚴密 監視中。 <br />\n<br />\n而北京共同社亦報導，中國海軍新聞官於24號表示，中國的海軍艦隊將駛往西太平洋進行 遠洋訓練，中國的海軍艦隊將穿越由沖繩,台灣及菲律賓所串成的第一島鏈駛向西太平洋 。 <br />\n<br />\n此次航行有可能是為了反制美國與台灣蔡英文政府間的互動。 該海軍艦隊從東海前往太平洋時，可能由沖繩近海處穿越。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://this.kiji.is/185369202138660869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthis.kiji.is%2F185369202138660869&d=dKoicb9uGzfvckZArvOw0QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=da980843\" target=\"_blank\">https://this.kiji.is/185369202138660869</a> [url]<a href=\"http://www.okinawatimes.co.jp/articles/-/77282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.okinawatimes.co.jp%2Farticles%2F-%2F77282&d=dKoicb9uGzfvckZArvOw0QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=018d3590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.okinawatimes.co.jp/articles/-/77282</a> <br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"77584a4a72a939b7266f330a38df986f90459f9a","tid":53774,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2094141a60ac02912b759b8280bc7107b513d75b","tid":53774,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae2504db8db3a84c0abf219439858347c1fc808","tid":53774,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-1